{"id": "unknown-2026-05-08-024", "date": "2026-05-08", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 19, "weekday": "Fri"}, "entities": {"companies": [], "customers": [], "suppliers": []}, "topics": ["oled_penetration"], "sentiment": {"label": "positive", "score": 0.75, "keywords": ["leading", "improve"]}, "importance": {"score": 0.65, "reasons": ["情緒極端"]}, "title": "Researchers show that the performance of the TADF-based OLEDs can be significantly improved by heating", "content": "<p>Researchers from the Kaunas University of Technology, the V. Lashkaryov Institute of Semiconductor Physics NAS of Ukraine, and Yuan Ze University, have shown that the performance of the TADF-based OLEDs can be significantly improved by heating, while extremely dependent on the applied biases. These findings are of interest, as normally high temperatures deteriorate the performance of light-emitting diodes, leading to excessive leakage currents, material degradation, and device failure.&nbsp;<", "sources": [{"name": "oled_info", "url": "https://www.oled-info.com/researchers-show-performance-tadf-based-oleds-can-be-significantly-improved", "type": "rss"}]}
{"id": "csot-2026-05-08-025", "date": "2026-05-08", "time_tags": {"year": 2026, "quarter": "Q2", "month": 5, "week": 19, "weekday": "Fri"}, "entities": {"companies": ["csot", "tcl"], "customers": ["tcl"], "suppliers": ["csot"]}, "topics": ["oled_penetration"], "sentiment": {"label": "neutral", "score": 0.0, "keywords": []}, "importance": {"score": 0.9, "reasons": ["多公司提及", "供應鏈上下游同時提及"]}, "title": "TCL CSOT: the main building in our upcoming T8 8.6-Gen inkjet printing IT AMOLED line has been topped out, ahead of schedule", "content": "<p>TCL CSOT has announced that the main building in its upcoming T8 8.6-Gen inkjet printing IT AMOLED Production line in Guangzhou has been topped out. The company is now starting to build the cleanrooms inside the building, install the power system, and then install the core equipment.</p><div class=\"align-center\">\n  \n  <a href=\"https://www.oled-info.com/sites/default/files/2026-05/TCL-CSOT-T8-inkjet-printing-oled-fab-building-topped-out.jpg\" target=\"_blank\">\n    \n    <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"h", "sources": [{"name": "oled_info", "url": "https://www.oled-info.com/tcl-csot-main-building-our-upcoming-t8-86-gen-inkjet-printing-it-amoled-line", "type": "rss"}]}
